<br>
You will be using 1 handed weapons 95% of the time post 55 unless you get something really nice like a Windblade. I'd suggest keeping everything maxed, but depending on how fast you level, that may not always be possible. I've spent lots of time ungrouped, beating on other people's mobs to up weapon skills in the past. I'd suggest going to Lake Rathe in one of the orc camp tents, and getting a shovel. It's about the fastest 2hb in the game. Ornate runed blade is nice to work up 2hs. <p><HTML><center>
