<br>
I would truly be lost without mine. It's a great tool for Executioner trial when you're fighting the boss mob. It lets me comfortably duo in valor with my cleric bot. It has made the difference between life and death in exp groups when the shaman/enchanter has gone LD.<br>
<br>
It's one of those tools that every warrior should eventually get in my opinion.<br>
<br>
EDIT: I'm saying yes, max your 2hb skill, because while you can proc on a miss, if you're not hitting at all, you're not keeping any aggro and somebody will get munched if you have a bad streak, with full skill in 2hb and no haste spell I can still put out about 45dps with a ToD which is plenty to keep up with the CHs my cleric needs to cast on me against an unslowed mob in PoV.<br>
